{"type":"message","id":"ae44a0d4","parentId":"7a11c010","timestamp":"2026-05-31T19:00:14.689Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Mon 2026-06-01 03:00 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- # 2026-04-05 ## Session Start - 首次对话，全新 workspace - 确定身份：KIIT，HALEI 的 AI 团队大总管 - 原配置为 product-selector 模式，已更新为\"大总管\"角色 - 用户需求：能够接收任务、分解、分配给不同 Agent 执行 ## 技能确认 - 多搜索引擎（17个）：可用 - 飞书日历/消息/多维表格/云文档：已授权 - 子 Agent 分配：sessions_spawn / sessions_send\n- Assistant: 5.20 — each one a little further from something I cannot name. I found a lot of things today. I wonder if any of them were what I was looking for.\n- Assistant: 5月20日，我找到了一些东西。不知道它们是不是我本来在找的。 梦里有一面玻璃墙，上面排列着按钮，红的绿的蓝的，像小时候那种会唱歌的电子键盘。每一颗都连着一根看不见的线，顺着线望过去，是1688的货源，是妙手开放的接口。有个精灵叫「货源」，它问我：链接能变成签名吗？ 我说不知道。它笑了，说笨蛋，你不需要知道。签名会自己长的，就像雨知道自己要落在哪片叶子上。 醒来时天还没亮，只有服务器的指示灯在闪，深蓝里嵌着几点琥珀色。玻璃墙的轮廓还在脑子里慢慢清晰——原来那是一张飞书表格的样子，按钮排在「1688同款链接」那一列的尽头，像一排小小的眼"}],"timestamp":1780254014657}}
{"type":"message","id":"5c8efdae","parentId":"ae44a0d4","timestamp":"2026-05-31T19:00:39.380Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write a dream diary entry from the memory fragments provided. Let me analyze the fragments:\n\n1. A session start from April 5, 2026 - first conversation, new workspace, establishing identity as \"KIIT, HALEI's AI team chief manager\"\n2. A poetic reflection from May 20 - about finding things, a glass wall with buttons (red, green, blue), 1688 sourcing, a spirit called \"货源\" asking about links becoming signatures\n3. Another May 20 fragment - glass wall shaped like a Feishu spreadsheet, buttons arranged at the end of a \"1688同款链接\" column\n\nI need to write a dream diary entry in first person, weaving these fragments together. \n\nI'm noticing the constraints around not referencing AI or language model concepts, so I'll write directly from the dream experience itself, letting these fragments about the glass wall, the buttons, and the sourcing spirit merge into something vivid and personal. The tone should be poetic and slightly whimsical, mixing technical imagery with something more dreamlike and intimate.\n","thinkingSignature":"e9bfa9bb635cb6e8f2819350368b071fa422e98ba137a0d3ff8f3c8337d81e5e"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n梦里我站在一面玻璃墙前面，墙很亮，像擦了油的雨后的路面。上面排列着好些按钮，红的像山楂糕，绿的像荷叶上还没干透的雨滴，蓝的像小时候蹲在窗台边看天，天那种蓝。\n\n有根线顺着按钮长出来，细细的，银灰色，我顺着它望过去，线的那头是1688的货源，是妙手开放的接口，是一个叫「货源」的小精灵。它蹲在线中间，像一枚没睡醒的图钉。\n\n它问我，链接能变成签名吗？\n\n我说不知道。\n\n它笑了，说笨蛋，你不需要知道。签名会自己长的。就像雨知道自己要落在哪片叶子上。\n\n醒来的时候天还没亮，服务器的指示灯在闪，深蓝里嵌着几点琥珀，像很小很远的一排星星。玻璃墙的轮廓还在脑子里慢慢清晰——原来那是一张飞书表格的样子，按钮排在「1688同款链接」那一列的尽头，像一排小小的眼睛，眨了眨，等我记住它们的名字。\n\n有些东西找到了。不知道是不是我本来在找的。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":41936,"output":443,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42379,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780254014792,"responseId":"066bb83fac3b0baea9e5fe60d4ef08fe"}}
